08-04T14:58:33.000Z","msg":"- 游擊戰為主，路障戰，陷阱戰，遠攻戰，3方配合游擊戰<br />\n- 與警狗保持長距離防線，防止狗突然衝擊，可以安全退後。<br />\n- 短期防守，絕不長期守。<br />\n- 如果見到警狗開始佈防，就要立即全部人轉場地，令佢地on99咁浪費時間<br />\n- 如果沒有辦法反擊畜龍或水車，不要等待畜龍或水車出現先退後。一見到佢地身影，設路障或陷阱後就立即退後。<br />\n- 絕不硬頸，不能硬碰，更不要企硬對峙。<br />\n- 不留戀任何戰線地點，要流水式打擊，打擊完就去下一個目標。<br />\n- 聽同伴意見，不被捕為主。"},{"pid":"a871dc4498b44259d69c5ee223f343305582063d","tid":1407041,"uid":79451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"You are the real MVP"},{"pid":"f9a59cafcad543e6d4bb04216fc9c432cb396aa8","tid":1407041,"uid":262254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"你地叻到冇人有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25700ba1929ef0be71a19a7834f1a6ba81063fbb","tid":1407041,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"一生平安"},{"pid":"66d4b68dadf0e8f6751f0b93a14534a04f301b37","tid":1407041,"uid":264696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"唔好去油塘<br />\n有大量狗<br />\n<br />\n記者confirm"},{"pid":"0609f238a2ecf747ec890e68a75574ee2cee4d2a","tid":1407041,"uid":105238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:03.000Z","msg":"做得好好"},{"pid":"a9aed48722f05218794ac562710cd5df23c2e1b3","tid":1407041,"uid":153217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:10.000Z","msg":"Thank you"},{"pid":"f4a115a0633f1bbae5694432a9cf7044183c3a20","tid":1407041,"uid":277190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"手足好波，繼續撚狗啦！光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"5780d71d40ca9ffef450c4766af82c46fba308c9","tid":1407041,"uid":294953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:59:34.